\s N’IGIHE KI GA MUKRISTO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd N’igihe ki ga mwene Data, ko mbon’ibihe birakuze, n’igihe ki ga ncuti yanje, ko mbona Umwami ari mukuza\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Kuko ni igihe cahanuwe, naco caramaze guseruka./.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.\bdit*\bdit Umugeni nawe ariteguye, Umwami \bdit*\bdit Yesu azohagarara avuge n’ijwi rirenga ati:\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit Ni muze yemwe bene Data niho tuzoba dukiz’amarira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd N’igihe ki bana b’Imana, ko mbon’ijambo ry’ubuhanuzi, iryo twari twarasezeraniwe, naryo ryaramaze guseruka\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Nuko rero ntidufyine ku gakiza twaronse k’ubuntu./.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Umugeni nawe ariteguye, Umwami Yesu azohagarara avuge n’ijwi rirenga ati: Ni muze yemwe bene Data niho tuzoba dukiz’amarira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd N’igihe ki yemwe shengero, nico gusab’Imana ukwizera, kandi tukagira n’ingeso nziza, ubwenge hamwe n’ukwirinda\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Kukw’ihanga ry’Uhoraho, tur’umuco n’umunyu w’iy’isi./.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Umugeni nawe ariteguye, Umwami Yesu azohagarara avuge n’ijwi rirenga ati: Ni muze yemwe bene Data niho tuzoba dukiz’amarira./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Kandi harahiriw’umuntu, yihanganira ibimugerageza, kuko niyarama, azohabwa ca gitsibo, kimwe c’ubugingo\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Ic’Imana yasezeraniye abazoba barabay’abahizi./.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Umugeni nawe ariteguye, Umwami Yesu azohagarara avuge n’ijwi rirenga ati: Ni muze yemwe bene Data niho tuzoba dukiz’amarira./.\bdit*
